HEADWORD: Gymnonoti
<hw>Gym`no*no"ti</hw> <pr>(j⟦icr⟧m`n⟦osl⟧*n⟦omac⟧"t⟦imac⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL. fr. Gr. <grk>gymno`s</grk> naked +
<grk>nw^tos</grk> the back.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The order of
